name: Monster Inc Goes Singing With Mike
description: One day, my mother showed the movie Monster Inc. I really enjoyed watching it, because there was a very funny mike. I really like when he sings and holds the mic, behind his silliness he is very good. My mother then showed me a picture of Moncter Inc for me to draw. When finished I added the mic in Mike's hand, and said that the monsters would go sing with Mike.
